msgstr "Tipul de legătură al canalului cerut nu este implementat"

#: tls/gnutls/gtlsconnection-gnutls.c:1208
#: tls/gnutls/gtlsconnection-gnutls.c:1268
#: tls/openssl/gtlsconnection-openssl.c:786
